<center>
<table width="600">
	<tr>
		<td>
			<h1 align="center">ImageScape</h1>
			<hr>			
		
			<p><b>Developed by:</b><br> Leiden University, The Netherlands </p>
			
			<p>
			<b>Features:</b><br> 
			- Features used in the systems are<br>
			1) Frequency histogram of calculated edge image,<br>
			2) Laplacian,<br>
			3) Gradient magnitude,<br>
			4) Local binary pattern,<br>
			5) Invariant moments,<br>
			6) Fourier descriptors
			</p>
			
			<p>
			<b>Matching:</b><br>
			1) Calculate distance on frequency histogram of the edge image<br>
			2) 20 matches are selected using the most informative pixels to minimize the misdetection rate.
			</p>
			
			<p>
			<b>Querying:</b><br>
			User can draw an outline of desire image or bring an icon that represent the objects/concepts he or she is looking for at desired location.
			</p>
			
			<p align="center">
			<i>Fig 1. Query window of ImageScape.</i><br>
			<i>
			<img border="0" src="images/imagescape/imagescape.jpg" width="697" height="527"><br>
			&nbsp;</i></p>
			
		</td>
	</tr>
